text: Insanity: doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results.Imagination is more important than knowledge.Imagination is everything. It is the preview of life's coming attractions.Life is like riding a bicycle. To keep your balance you must keep moving.If you can't explain it simply, you don't understand it well enough.The important thing is not to stop questioning. Curiosity has its own reason for existing.In the middle of difficulty lies opportunity.No problem can be solved from the same level of consciousness that created it.Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.Two things are infinite: the universe and human stupidity; and I'm not sure about the universe.
element:
Insanity: doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results.
Imagination is more important than knowledge.
Imagination is everything. It is the preview of life's coming attractions.
Life is like riding a bicycle. To keep your balance you must keep moving.
If you can't explain it simply, you don't understand it well enough.
The important thing is not to stop questioning. Curiosity has its own reason for existing.
In the middle of difficulty lies opportunity.
No problem can be solved from the same level of consciousness that created it.
Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.
Two things are infinite: the universe and human stupidity; and I'm not sure about the universe.
